author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Stream title in English: “Cooking Simulator ☆ Lovingly make a menu”
Also opened with that nice BGM named "Hana ni hanasaku kimitachi e"
Also the stream had a good BGM selection... The BGM at gameplay is the same of "Rushia's Cooking - Halloween Pancakes" 

Totally an intense and wonderful stream... And First time with Rushia playing "Cooking Simulator" :_ちょうちょ:
Fortunately is a game where hand pulse is the key for the perfection... Well, who needs the perfection? We have Rushia-daitenshi already... :_ハート:

And today's menu, between fried fish with lemon (Like Steak mignon) and Tomato Soup... We have something to say: “Full stomach, Happy heart” :_きゅん:

Even at gaming Rushia is a great at cooking, despite the broken plates.
Personally talking, I've also noticed from someone preparatory school girl who has the poor cooking ever... She would be learn how to cook from the Pink-purple... Well... Turquoise haired girl with odangos and dokuro and butterflies ornaments. :_ちょうちょ:

And just at mid of reading Superchats at "Supaachaato Orei Time", Youtube and Google fell down. At least we were here until the end of Rushia's streams.
When YouTube returned to normal, LiveChat was already running... 3 Akai Naisupas, 1 Green Naisupa and 1 Blue Naisupa at the last 5 minutes...

At these three messages: "Aa Supacha Arigatou Gozaimasu, saigo no Orei no Matteru kudasai" :_るんるん:

Well... The "Saigo no..." would be at the Next Stream. :_ハート:
